00:06:43.980 --> 00:06:45.980
Miss Zhang, you are looking at jade.

00:06:47.320 --> 00:06:48.940
Do not look aimlessly
and buy recklessly.

00:06:48.940 --> 00:06:49.980
Let me tell you.

00:06:50.540 --> 00:06:52.220
There are so many fakes nowadays.

00:06:52.380 --> 00:06:53.980
If you buy, you must buy something good.

00:06:54.300 --> 00:06:56.380
Let me show you the one from my family.

00:06:56.980 --> 00:06:57.620
Mingzhu.

00:06:58.260 --> 00:06:58.860
Come here.

00:06:58.860 --> 00:07:00.620
Show Aunt Zhang your bangle.

00:07:02.420 --> 00:07:02.980
Come on.

00:07:03.040 --> 00:07:05.060
- Wait a moment.
- Where is this water coming from?

00:07:06.020 --> 00:07:06.900
Lobby manager!

00:07:07.700 --> 00:07:08.500
Lobby manager!

00:07:08.500 --> 00:07:09.420
Let me tell you.

00:07:09.420 --> 00:07:11.500
Nanxi Hotel
is not doing well these days.

00:07:11.500 --> 00:07:13.420
Guests are shouting everywhere.

00:07:13.420 --> 00:07:15.020
There is no manners at all.

00:07:15.020 --> 00:07:17.180
Why is there water all over the floor?

00:07:17.180 --> 00:07:18.860
