00:11:14.900 --> 00:11:15.740
Thank you.

00:11:17.820 --> 00:11:18.620
All right.

00:11:19.140 --> 00:11:20.660
Today is a happy day.

00:11:20.660 --> 00:11:21.020
Yes.

00:11:21.020 --> 00:11:21.980
Let us

00:11:22.140 --> 00:11:23.260
