It's all cooked into soup.

00:31:55.580 --> 00:31:56.500
Why so many questions?

00:31:56.500 --> 00:31:57.860
Isn't that for our daughter?

00:31:59.500 --> 00:32:00.700
This one's for that poor woman.

00:32:02.940 --> 00:32:04.900
I must have owed her in a past life.

00:32:04.900 --> 00:32:06.340
I'll never repay it in this one.

00:32:07.180 --> 00:32:07.820
Mom.

00:32:08.100 --> 00:32:09.500
You really are beautiful and kind.

