I've had a brain puncture.

00:32:12.700 --> 00:32:13.700
Beautiful and kind...

00:32:14.700 --> 00:32:15.750
There's something wrong with me.

00:32:39.460 --> 00:32:40.140
Zhidong.

00:32:40.260 --> 00:32:41.820
Are you staying at the hospital tonight?

