00:36:55.300 --> 00:36:56.300
Shen Minghui.

00:36:57.140 --> 00:37:00.020
You don't pass exams by praying.

00:37:00.660 --> 00:37:01.900
You're very bright.

00:37:02.700 --> 00:37:04.220
So why can't you put that energy

00:37:04.220 --> 00:37:05.700
into studying?

00:37:06.420 --> 00:37:08.460
Lu Bing has strong grades.

00:37:09.020 --> 00:37:10.700
So you should work even harder

00:37:10.700 --> 00:37:12.860
and try to catch up with her,
shouldn't you?

00:37:15.260 --> 00:37:16.020
Mr. Hu.

00:37:17.500 --> 00:37:18.940
Your grades were excellent.

00:37:22.940 --> 00:37:24.100
So why are you still single?

00:37:28.180 --> 00:37:28.980
Quiet down.

00:37:33.500 --> 00:37:35.140
Stop worrying about whether L2 or L1

00:37:35.140 --> 00:37:36.140
will change.

00:37:37.380 --> 00:37:38.660
Will Feng Meiqi change?

00:37:41.670 --> 00:37:42.510
Look at the question.

00:37:42.900 --> 00:37:43.580
Which one?

00:37:44.340 --> 00:37:44.900
C.

00:37:55.180 --> 00:37:55.700
Mom.

00:37:55.900 --> 00:37:57.860
You look much better today.

00:37:57.860 --> 00:37:58.460
Okay.

00:37:58.620 --> 00:37:59.460
Higher? Is that okay?

00:37:59.460 --> 00:38:00.660
Yes, son.

00:38:01.300 --> 00:38:02.020
That's good.

00:38:06.660 --> 00:38:08.700
My son has worked so hard.

00:38:08.980 --> 00:38:09.500
It's fine.

00:38:10.180 --> 00:38:11.060
Wipe your hands.

00:38:11.060 --> 00:38:12.880
Your sister will be here soon,
then we'll eat.

00:38:23.460 --> 00:38:24.100
Zhidong.

00:38:24.420 --> 00:38:24.940
Zhixia.

00:38:25.140 --> 00:38:26.380
Hurry, go home and rest.

00:38:26.380 --> 00:38:26.750
I'm here.

00:38:27.100 --> 00:38:29.740
I… I don't think I'll make it to work.

00:38:29.750 --> 00:38:31.540
It's still early,
you can sleep for half an hour.

00:38:31.540 --> 00:38:32.580
Yes, at noon

00:38:32.580 --> 00:38:34.700
take a short nap at the office.

00:38:34.700 --> 00:38:35.740
Mom, stop worrying.

00:38:35.740 --> 00:38:36.860
Our shift is easy.

00:38:36.860 --> 00:38:37.420
All right.

00:38:37.420 --> 00:38:38.700
Zhixia, pour the water, please.

00:38:38.940 --> 00:38:39.660
Slow down.

00:38:39.660 --> 00:38:41.020
Yes, a bit slower.

00:38:42.260 --> 00:38:43.460
Your son

00:38:43.700 --> 00:38:44.900
has really grown sensible.

00:38:46.540 --> 00:38:48.700
Of course, he's my boy.

00:38:53.180 --> 00:38:55.140
This is the fish soup
my dad made for you.

00:38:55.620 --> 00:38:57.540
He didn't add any MSG. Have a smell.

00:38:58.940 --> 00:38:59.580
Too oily.

00:39:00.660 --> 00:39:02.500
Drink a little. It's good for nutrition.

00:39:10.980 --> 00:39:11.820
Mingzhu.

00:39:12.900 --> 00:39:13.700
You're here.

00:39:14.380 --> 00:39:15.820
My mom made some chicken soup.

00:39:16.020 --> 00:39:16.980
It's really nourishing.

00:39:18.660 --> 00:39:20.180
Your... Your mom…

00:39:20.540 --> 00:39:23.260
Your mom brought chicken soup for me?

00:39:24.860 --> 00:39:27.540
Your mom is such a kind person.

00:39:28.940 --> 00:39:30.060
I need to thank her.

00:39:30.540 --> 00:39:32.260
Please thank her for me later.

00:39:32.260 --> 00:39:32.900
Okay.

00:39:33.580 --> 00:39:34.620
I'll ladle you a bowl.

00:39:36.860 --> 00:39:37.420
Go ahead.

00:39:52.380 --> 00:39:52.940
Here.

00:39:57.740 --> 00:39:58.980
It smells wonderful.

00:39:59.540 --> 00:40:02.020
It really does smell wonderful.

00:40:13.300 --> 00:40:14.140
It tastes good.

00:40:15.380 --> 00:40:17.020
It's really good.

00:40:17.420 --> 00:40:18.980
I served my mom fish soup earlier,

00:40:18.980 --> 00:40:20.150
and she said it was too oily.

00:40:23.180 --> 00:40:24.300
There's a drumstick too.

00:40:24.420 --> 00:40:25.700
Go on and eat it, all right?

00:40:27.660 --> 00:40:29.500
Okay, okay.

00:40:40.500 --> 00:40:41.380
All my life,

00:40:42.340 --> 00:40:44.620
I've never eaten a drumstick.

00:40:52.660 --> 00:40:53.340
Delicious.

00:40:55.340 --> 00:40:56.100
Delicious.

00:41:00.340 --> 00:41:01.100
Delicious.

00:41:03.980 --> 00:41:06.340
I went through
the gates of death this time.

00:41:09.500 --> 00:41:10.300
It was worth it.

00:41:14.180 --> 00:41:14.940
Worth it.

00:41:20.180 --> 00:41:20.980
Mingzhu.

00:41:21.420 --> 00:41:23.180
You don't look very pregnant at all.

00:41:24.700 --> 00:41:25.420
The baby's there.

00:41:26.420 --> 00:41:27.180
It really is.

00:41:29.620 --> 00:41:30.700
Thank you for today.

00:41:31.220 --> 00:41:32.140
Once you arrived,

00:41:32.700 --> 00:41:34.180
Madam Yu suddenly looked much better.

00:41:35.540 --> 00:41:36.540
You said it yourself.

00:41:36.540 --> 00:41:38.360
We don't need
to be so polite with each other.

00:41:42.540 --> 00:41:43.980
To be honest, my mom

00:41:45.020 --> 00:41:45.980
has had a hard life.

00:41:47.380 --> 00:41:49.020
She wasn't exaggerating at all just now.

00:41:49.860 --> 00:41:51.700
She really has never eaten a drumstick.

00:41:53.180 --> 00:41:54.420
The family was poor back then.

00:41:55.180 --> 00:41:56.150
They couldn't afford it.

00:41:56.740 --> 00:41:58.220
After Zhidong and I were born,

00:41:59.380 --> 00:42:00.700
she had to put us first.

00:42:01.820 --> 00:42:04.220
Over time, she simply got used to it.

00:42:04.220 --> 00:42:05.420
It became muscle memory.

00:42:05.900 --> 00:42:06.820
She'd think she

00:42:07.500 --> 00:42:10.860
liked chewing on necks
or gnawing on feet.

00:42:11.700 --> 00:42:12.860
My mom is the same.

00:42:13.700 --> 00:42:14.660
Growing up,

00:42:14.980 --> 00:42:17.020
the drumsticks always
went to my brother and me.

00:42:20.300 --> 00:42:21.020
Yes.

00:42:22.180 --> 00:42:23.180
Same world,

00:42:24.180 --> 00:42:25.100
same kind of mom.

00:42:26.940 --> 00:42:27.580
Oh, right.

00:42:28.180 --> 00:42:29.340
Something was odd today.

00:42:29.980 --> 00:42:32.580
Your mom actually made soup for my mom.

00:42:32.860 --> 00:42:34.580
She's sharp-tongued but soft-hearted.

00:42:36.140 --> 00:42:37.140
Without my mom,

00:42:38.260 --> 00:42:39.860
I wouldn't have dared to keep this baby.

00:42:40.140 --> 00:42:42.340
And I definitely wouldn't have dared
to be a single mom.

